    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 9800 - IC BUS SERVICE MANUAL - FLOOR COVERING - INSPECTION
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="inspect" graphiccount="0">
        <title>INSPECTION</title>
        <para>The floor trim, mounting hardware that secures the floor trim and the step thread should be inspected
            weekly. Mounting screws should be tightened if found loose. The entrance door stepwell area and driver's
            area should be kept clean of any foreign debris (
            <hotlnk document="s47001y_41.xml" xrefid="f4700174">Figure 67</hotlnk>).
        </para>
    </svcproc>
